---
const year = new Date().getFullYear();
---
<footer class="border-t border-gray-200 bg-gray-50 dark:bg-slate-900 dark:border-slate-700 mt-12">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 py-8">
    <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-3 gap-6 text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-slate-400">
      <div>
        <p class="font-semibold text-gray-800 dark:text-slate-200 mb-2">WorkAuthUS</p>
        <p>Plain-language answers to US work authorization questions, with links to the actual law.</p>
      </div>
      <div>
        <p class="font-semibold text-gray-800 dark:text-slate-200 mb-2">Pages</p>
        <ul class="space-y-1">
          <li><a href="/topics" class="hover:text-blue-700 dark:hover:text-blue-400 underline">Browse Topics</a></li>
          <li><a href="/find-legal-help" class="hover:text-blue-700 dark:hover:text-blue-400 underline">Find Legal Help</a></li>
          <li><a href="/about" class="hover:text-blue-700 dark:hover:text-blue-400 underline">About</a></li>
          <li><a href="/contribute" class="hover:text-blue-700 dark:hover:text-blue-400 underline">Contribute</a></li>
          <li><a href="/changelog" class="hover:text-blue-700 dark:hover:text-blue-400 underline">Changelog</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div>
        <p class="font-semibold text-gray-800 dark:text-slate-200 mb-2">Disclaimer</p>
        <p>
          This site provides <strong>legal information, not legal advice.</strong> Nothing here creates an attorney-client relationship. For advice about your specific situation, consult a licensed immigration attorney or accredited representative.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <p class="mt-6 text-xs text-gray-400 dark:text-slate-600">
      Content licensed under <a href="https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="underline hover:text-gray-600">CC BY 4.0</a>.
      Code licensed under <a href="https://opensource.org/licenses/MIT" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="underline hover:text-gray-600">MIT</a>.
      &copy; {year} WorkAuthUS contributors.
    </p>
  </div>
</footer>
